usage: git sandbox [<options>]

Create and manage a git sandbox.

    -h|--help               display help
    --reset                 reset repos
    --sm                    create submodules
    --skus                  create SKUs
    --work                  create some work in all modules
    --vr                    create version resources
    
example:
    git sandbox --reset --sm --skus     # create a sandbox with submodules and SKUs
    git sandbox --vr --work             # commit version resources and some work
